properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters from Fernandina Beach to St. Augustine FL out 20 NM; Coastal waters from St. Augustine to Flagler Beach FL out 20 NM; Coastal waters from Altamaha Sound to Fernandina Beach FL out 20 NM
properties.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued February 12 at 2:37PM EST until February 13 at 8:00AM EST by NWS Jacksonville FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...Dense fog will reduce visibility to less than 1 mile.

* WHERE...Coastal waters from Altamaha Sound to Fernandina Beach
FL out 20 NM, Coastal waters from Fernandina Beach to St.
Augustine FL out 20 NM and Coastal waters from St. Augustine
to Flagler Beach FL out 20 NM.

* WHEN...Until 8 AM EST Thursday.

* IMPACTS...Low visibility will make navigation difficult.
properties.instruction:
If you must navigate, proceed with caution. Use proper fog
signals. Make sure all running lights are on. Remember to use
your radar and compass.

NWSheadline: DENSE FOG ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 8 AM EST THURSDAY
